; concept-audio-human-13-observed.fk -- bounded offline replay of human speech.
;
; Every transcript below is the exact unprompted whisper-cli byte string from
; a neutral numeric WAV path.  Candidate ids are the complete 10,000-label
; Form scan in detector order, not a curated confusion set.  The replay gate
; runs those exact transcript bytes through the detector again and requires
; bit-identical candidate-id lists.  Misses are first-class rows.
; witnessed: 2026-07-18 -> 13 acquired, 8 expected present, 5 retained misses
; preludes: form/form-stdlib/core.fk model/concept-10000-data.fk model/concept-10000.fk model/concept-semantics-10000-data.fk model/concept-semantics-10000.fk cognition/nl-lenses-13-data.fk cognition/nl-lenses-13.fk cognition/concept-nl-semantic-13-metadata.fk cognition/concept-nl-semantic-13-offsets.fk cognition/concept-nl-semantic-13.fk cognition/concept-nl-semantic-13-runtime.fk cognition/concept-text-senses-10000-metadata.fk cognition/concept-text-senses-10000-offsets.fk cognition/concept-text-senses-10000.fk cognition/concept-text-detection-13.fk cognition/concept-text-detection-13-runtime.fk model/concept-audio-human-13.fk

